  "title": "Account Manager",
  "description": "<p>Location: Ubi | Full-time </p><p>Looking to break into sales or hopping from retail sales to office with no prior experience? Join EdgeProp.sg, Singapore’s leading property portal — where new joiners thrive.</p><p>One of our top rookies achieved $10,000 take home in just 4 months of joining, starting from zero experience. With the right attitude, it’s possible.<br /></p><p>What You’ll Do:</p><ul><li>Manage and support real estate agent clients</li><li>Sell digital marketing tools & property solutions</li><li>Build trust and follow through on client needs</li><li>Actively hunt for prospects and pitch our solutions at events, roadshows, and outreach locations (Toa Payoh)</li><li>Curate and maintain social media content (simple posting)</li><li>Ad-hoc duties as assigned</li><li></li></ul><p>We Provide:</p><ul><li>Structured training to get you started fast</li><li>Warm leads — no cold starts (existing work phone provided)</li><li>Guidance from team lead and team work environment</li></ul><p>You Bring:</p><ul><li>No experience needed — just drive and a go-getter attitude</li><li>People skills and a willingness to learn</li><li>Interest in sales, digital, or real estate</li><li>Energy and youth</li></ul><p>Why Join Us?</p><ul><li>Competitive base + incentives</li><li>Transport & entertainment allowance</li><li>Medical, dental & insurance benefits</li><li>15 days annual leave</li><li>Fast-paced, supportive team with real career growth</li><li>5-day work week for better work-life balance</li></ul>",
